response.original_title: Munda Nyuringu: A Film of the Fringe Dwellers of the Goldfields
response.overview: Aboriginal people on the Goldfields of Kalgoorlie, Western Australia (Australia) recount their history, speaking amidst living conditions of grinding poverty next to the gold and nickel mines and uranium development.
response.tagline: He's taken the land. He believes it is his. He won't give it back.
response.title: Munda Nyuringu: A Film of the Fringe Dwellers of the Goldfields
